$interpreted: Nigel: Incoming! You two be care...
Nigel: ful...... Eh?
Izumi: Ooh, you finally awake~?
Izumi: The monster is already dead~
Nigel: Dead? Did you defeat it by yourself...
Nigel: Ah, right! Yamitsuki...!

Izumi: Rest assured. I inspected her. She is alright as well.
... I settled her down on the side for now so she can rest.
Nigel: I'll go see her...
Izumi: I heard that your name is Nigel?
Izumi: This name......
Izumi: So you're the leader of the demihuman organization that caused the Kingdom of the Sun capitol to crash?
Nigel: ... Who in the world are you...
Izumi: I'm a demihuman from the East Alliance. My name is Izumi~

Izumi: The real purpose of my trip to Atlas,
is that I want to return to the place we demihumans once called home.
Nigel: What?
Izumi: I would like to follow you. What about you? Are you willing to accept me?
Izumi: Hoho~ So that happened... How surprising...
Yamitsuki: You guys...
Nigel: Yamitsuki, you're awake.
Nigel: Let's go back. We are going to bring everybody here.
Yamitsuki: ... I don't understand...
Nigel: I've decided. From now on, this castle will be our stronghold. We are going to restore Atlas' past glory.
Yamitsuki: Why are we doing this all of a sudden——
Nigel: Also, this guy is called Izumi. He just saved us back there. Starting today, he will be one of us.
Nigel: Past misunderstandings shall stay in the past. That goes for both of you.
Yamitsuki: Nigel!
Nigel: That's all I wanted to say.
Yamitsuki: Wait, listen to me... Nigel!
Izumi: (Though different from the original plan, this is still quite enjoyable~)

Izumi: (Nigel......
Show me, to what place can your perseverance of demihumans take you.)
